150
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:03,679
and the scenes of people dancing.

151
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,360
That's all?

152
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:10,279
And the dishes of Zhen Qiang.

153
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,080
My boss

154
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:16,200
is quite nice,

155
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,559
but I often feel like

156
00:13:17,559 --> 00:13:19,600
