of each other's difficulties,

175
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:55,080
and not to put any pressure or burden
to each other.

176
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,440
Owing nothing to each other.

177
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:57,600
I do admire the pattern

178
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,360
