180
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:04,440
between colleagues.

181
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:13,440
What about you?
What kind of relationship do you want?

182
00:14:17,360 --> 00:14:21,200
I hope the person I love

183
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,360
is my best friend.

184
00:14:24,039 --> 00:14:26,320
We don't need to be one hundred percent alike.

185
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,519
We can have our own interests and hobbies,

186
00:14:28,519 --> 00:14:30,399
but we are willing

187
00:14:30,399 --> 00:14:33,200
to experience new things together
for each other.

188
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,840
If I see

189
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,759
