192
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,399
If I see something delicious,

193
00:14:44,399 --> 00:14:46,559
I would take her to try it.

194
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:49,120
How is it, is the food good today?

195
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,200
Very happy.

196
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:52,879
I hope to go see beautiful scenery

197
00:14:53,519 --> 00:14:54,559
with the person I like.

198
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:57,840
Even though I may have seen
this scenery many times,

199
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,840
